<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
<title>收款账单查询</title>
<meta name="menu" content="FinanceMenu"/>
<meta name="heading" content="收款账单查询">
</head>

<body>
<script type="text/javascript">
